		<title>库克看了都沉默：用 Mac 触控板称西瓜，结果超出预期！｜TrackWeight 实测</title>
		<link>https://www.appinn.com/trackweight/</link>
					<comments>https://www.appinn.com/trackweight/#comments</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[青小蛙]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 22 Jul 2025 09:31:56 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[macOS]]></category>
